    <item>
      <title>SUPERVISOR_TEAM_PREFIX</title>
      <link>https://iboard.github.io/ematrix/emie/features/2025-10-07-supervisor-team-prefix/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://iboard.github.io/ematrix/emie/features/2025-10-07-supervisor-team-prefix/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://iboard.github.io/ematrix&#34;&gt;ematrix&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&#34;https://iboard.github.io/ematrix/emie&#34;&gt;emie&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&#34;https://iboard.github.io/ematrix/emie/features&#34;&gt;features&lt;/a&gt; | SUPERVISOR_TEAM_PREFIX&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When the env &lt;code&gt;SUPERVISOR_TEAM_PREFIX&lt;/code&gt; is set to &lt;code&gt;by_team&lt;/code&gt; (which is the default)&#xA;the supervisor of a person is set to the first team-leader of the first team&#xA;the person is a member of.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Other than that, the setting can be a fieldname of the HR-import record.&#xA;If set to &lt;code&gt;Team - &lt;/code&gt;, then on import the team leader of a team beginning with&#xA;&lt;code&gt;Team - &lt;/code&gt; is assigned as supervisor for all members of this team.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
